	     <tr><td valign="top" id="fs8" class="mform"><span id="notbold">By:</span> <a href="/db/poster.html?user=169747"><span id=" ">Korasak</span></a><br /><span id="notbold">402 posts<br /><span id="notbold">Score:</span> Default [2.18]</td><td valign=top class="mform" width="100%"><p>Unfortunately what you do not realize is that most guilds go by dkp, and that if the said class doesn't have these other ft items so he isn't capped(see:emp ssra shield), then he will no doubt bid on it. Shaman won it today, if i look at the classes on it tho, i can see that every class there can make good use of its stats and ft except for perhaps a ranger who should be using a bow ~ <br/><br/>So in conclusion there really is no point in writing whole essays trying to discuss this since the guilds that kill it are in no way affected by you whatsoever and will just do what they always do to award items,dkp for example etc etc<br/><br/>If on the other hand your just looking to debate people on it i only suggest that you stop wasting your time, and find something relevent to argue about.</p>&nbsp;<br /></td></tr>
